SELECT 'ChangeBlockOnSalesOrderScheduleLine' || '::' || "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock_Changes"."ID" AS "ID",
       "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock"."ID"                                           AS "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock",
       "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."ID"                                                AS "SalesOrderScheduleLine",
       "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock_Changes"."Time"                                 AS "Time",
       "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock_Changes"."ChangedBy"                            AS "ExecutedBy",
       "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock_Changes"."Attribute"                            AS "ChangedAttribute",
       "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock_Changes"."ExecutionType"                        AS "ExecutionType",
       "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock"."BlockType"                                    AS "BlockType",
       "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock_Changes"."OldValue"                             AS "OldValue",
       "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock_Changes"."NewValue"                             AS "NewValue"
FROM "o_custom_SalesOrderScheduleLine" AS "SalesOrderScheduleLine"
         LEFT JOIN "o_custom_SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock" AS "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock"
                   ON "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."ID" = "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock"."SalesOrderScheduleLine_ID"
         LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock" AS "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock_Changes"
                   ON "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock"."ID" = "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock_Changes"."ObjectID"
WHERE "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock_Changes"."Attribute" = 'LatestBlockReason'
  AND "SalesOrderScheduleLineBlock_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL
